init_text: An alien has kidnapped Matt Damon, not knowing what lengths humanity goes through to retrieve him whenever he goes missing.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The aliens are determined to figure out what makes Matt Damon so special that thousands of people would risk their lives to get him back.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: So they come up with a plan to clone him, but unfortunately for them the cloning machine malfunctions.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: So the aliens have no choice but to keep all of these clones locked in a cage.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They will then send that one back to Earth and announce to the world that Matt Damon has been found.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: So they dress him up as Matt Damon and send him back to Earth.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: All is well for a little while.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They just don't seem to be the same.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He gets along with the aliens and enjoys his life.
